column2: Q1. How would you feel if the system provides secure online club registration?
column3: Q2. How would you feel if login authentication is secure and reliable?
column4: Q3.How would you feel if club leaders can create new events online?
column5: Q4.  How would you feel if club leaders can view and track club budget balances?
column6: Q5. How would you feel if the system sends automatic notifications for approvals, rejections, or updates?
column7: Q6. The addition of Accessibility features such as color contrast , highlighted text etc.
column8: Q7.  How would you feel if the event creation process is efficient and guided (wizard)?
column9: Q8. How would you feel if the system provides real-time updates on budget spending?
column10: Q9. How would you feel if there is a searchable venue database (location, size, availability)?
column11: Q10. How would you feel if you can RSVP to register for events easily?
column12: Q11. How would you feel if you can export club financial data to CSV files?
column13: Q12. How would you feel if interested students can apply to join a club online?
column14: Q13. How would you feel if you have a personal dashboard showing upcoming events, budget graphs, and reminders?
column15: Q14. How would you feel if you receive mobile push notifications for critical updates?
column16: Q15. How would you feel if the system sends reminder alerts before your “interested” events?
column17: Q16. How would you feel if the system recommends clubs that might interest you?
column18: Q17. A section to highlight trending Clubs
column19: Q18. The abillity for club members  to message each other.
column20: Q19. How would you feel about getting points/awards (badges/titles) for participating in club events
